And I'm still a noob, only been in EQ since October, and I learn new things everyday, both in the game and about the game. <br>
<br>
I try to not give up on people, even if I take a break sometimes.  People can and will continually surprise you, in both directions.  I form opinions and I dare to make judgements, but I can also be effectively argued with, talked to, and often I can learn things that I didn't know before. <br>
