<br>
It's not always worth your trouble to work with someone, no.  You have to have enough investment sometimes that you're willing to continue to deal with something.  <br>
<br>
I'm here, in the game, and on these boards, because I enjoy playing a game.  I like keeping good company with folk, I like role-playing a bit, getting experience and seeing stuff, and I am unabashedly a fashion junkie in addition to getting excited when I get to wear a piece of loot I've never even heard of, never mind seen before. <br>
I'm certainly not here to make money, lol, and this place isn't organized enough for me to care about competition as a thing in itself.  When I want competition, I go play a competitive game, and kick someone's ass on the chessboard, or in a boardgame or, or with cards. <br>
